#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.audex.appdata.xml:6
msgid "Audex"
msgstr "Audex"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.audex.appdata.xml:7
msgid "Grab the audio from your CD-ROMs"
msgstr "Sasi (grab) le audio ex tu CD-Roms"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.audex.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"Audex is a CD ripper application. It lets you extract the audio from your "
"CDs to let you listen to them on your computer and your other devices. It "
"includes CDDB and MusicBrainz integrations to fetch the metadata and covers "
"for your CDs if available."
msgstr ""
"Audex es un application per rippar CD. Il te permitte extraher le audio ex "
"tu CDs, te permitte ascoltar los sur tu computator e sur tu altere "
"dispositivos. Illo include integrationes de  CDDB e de MusicBrainz pro "
"trovar metadatos  e coperturas per tu CDs, si disponibile."

