#~ msgid ""
#~ "The general usage of Audex is self-explanatory. With the first start "
#~ "Audex scans your system for common encoders and creates a common set of "
#~ "profiles automatically for you."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Le uso general de Audex es auto-explicatori. Con le prime initio Aude "
#~ "scande tu systema per codificatores commun e crea automaticamente per te "
#~ "un insimul de profilos"
